{"tid":650244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"懷疑九巴涉違反車廠地契契約","createTime":"2018-05-02T07:00:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T14:00:54.000Z","uid":72280,"like":79,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0aa882f2251023311ed42f7fecd22937c2a0974f","tid":650244,"uid":72280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T07:00:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/02/142815_47100739fe4a9a347ea3afaace3f37e9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F02%2F142815_47100739fe4a9a347ea3afaace3f37e9.png&h=92668183&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n九巴現提供非專利巴士維修檢查服務。詳情及服務計劃如下：<br />\n服務時間：星期一至星期六，上午9:00至下午4:00 (公眾假期除外)<br />\n查詢及預約電話：2686 2723 (李小姐)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.kmb.hk/tc/services/repairbus.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.kmb.hk%2Ftc%2Fservices%2Frepairbus.html&d=FtnGZSQXw2cpUIpZEyFXyp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=984f552e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.kmb.hk/tc/services/repairbus.html</a><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n今日打去問過相關人士<br />\n佢話服務會是九巴車廠進行<br />\n<br />\n於是好奇查下九巴有咩車廠維修中心<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/02/144308_853d05d17c49bedbfa8f600c67d2c567.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F02%2F144308_853d05d17c49bedbfa8f600c67d2c567.png&h=3ad9c254&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/02/144310_c82b206be43e5baed143c423cb0ea944.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F02%2F144310_c82b206be43e5baed143c423cb0ea944.png&h=e57dd3e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當中發現有依兩間車廠的地契係受制於九巴兩分専利權文件<br />\n分別係<br />\n<br />\n九巴屯門總修中心（KMB Overhaul Centre），俗稱KOC或82廠，位於屯門區屯門市地段82號<br />\n九巴九龍灣車廠<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/02/144500_90f70b7b5981a9e986c0861954d77e4f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F02%2F144500_90f70b7b5981a9e986c0861954d77e4f.png&h=49e2f0d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後去左HKU library 睇番個兩份專利權文件<br />\n原來兩個廠只是淮作專利巴士的日常維修，停泊用途"},{"pid":"b679419a10703e6dd1985b7fe6d63146c4e1b903","tid":650244,"uid":72280,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T07:14:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68631507a19644ad8e0a8f2978eed30c2d63a7dd","tid":650244,"uid":41678,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T07:17:25.000Z","msg":"可能人地比左lease modification premium 呢"},{"pid":"98825ae4cadf944d9003931a15ef79f2ba7d30d0","tid":650244,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T07:18:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f968314bbf844e93bc187ecbfddcfeca2acecca2","tid":650244,"uid":72280,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"68631507a19644ad8e0a8f2978eed30c2d63a7dd","tid":650244,"uid":41678,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T07:17:25.000Z","msg":"可能人地比左lease modification premium 呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T07:45:56.000Z","msg":"好似都是巴士廠用地"},{"pid":"4585dab2f5a5d7204c888393bd1313c19240a84a","tid":650244,"uid":72280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T07:51:58.000Z","msg":"25/6/1997 交上去個堆 modification letter 似係當年政府將土地由crown property 轉為hksar property 個堆租約更新文件"},{"pid":"11f25cd7f8db0491261aed4b73bc5d7c82c1c619","tid":650244,"uid":86433,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4585dab2f5a5d7204c888393bd1313c19240a84a","tid":650244,"uid":72280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T07:51:58.000Z","msg":"25/6/1997 交上去個堆 modification letter 似係當年政府將土地由crown property 轉為hksar property 個堆租約更新文件"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T09:23:14.000Z","msg":"比錢查land reg最實際<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" 