=FtnGZSQXw2cpUIpZEyFXyp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=9b75b235\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180502/mobile/bkn-20180502195628568-0502_00822_001.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n運輸署發言人回覆指，已根據香港法例第230章《公共巴士服務條例》第20條，在2018年2月批准九巴使用其位於沙田及屯門指定兩所車廠為非專營巴士提供維修檢查服務<br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來運輸署又官商勾結發批文<br />\n但點解佢地無入紙去改個分地契呢🤣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T08:36:22.000Z","msg":"咁我係味可以拎住分地契去地政總署開 file?"},{"pid":"17d85fcde75a8bbf257aa7c1b0ea637ed8dfdcb3","tid":650244,"uid":36324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2f28478d51edb9e461e71103dbdb060ad92a4cf","tid":650244,"uid":72280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11c2544e0e0daf42cb6543b632248f5454686c74","tid":650244,"uid":36324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T07:21:16.000Z","msg":"1997 轉 government lease 同續期要 modification letter 咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇咗咁多份 land search 都冇乜見過<br />\n<br />\n唔係 by legislation 有 automatic effect 咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T08:24:42.000Z","msg":"FYI<br />\n<a href=\"https://bkb.mpweekly.com/cu0001/20161230-18018\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbkb.mpweekly.com%2Fcu0001%2F20161230-18018&d=FtnGZSQXw2cpUIpZEyFXyp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=1cbe5bc8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bkb.mpweekly.com/cu0001/20161230-18018</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>1898英國接收新界後，將新界土地由永業權轉為承租權，由政府核實其契據後發出集體官契，其租用期權99年至1997年6月28日為止。本港地契批租年期不一，新界及九龍大多為99年，1997年到期後，英殖民政府批租土地的年限為 2047 年6月30日；一些港島土地租期長達999年，太古城地契長至2899年。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nBy legislation 過渡的主要係南九龍及香港用地"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T08:38:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hklii.hk/eng/hk/legis/ord/150/cur.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhklii.hk%2Feng%2Fhk%2Flegis%2Ford%2F150%2Fcur.html&d=FtnGZSQXw2cpUIpZEyFXyp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=023abbc8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hklii.hk/eng/hk/legis/ord/150/cur.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n根據我僅有所學，無 by legislation 續租係講緊 1984 年後開始有 lease 已經批到 1997 年 6 月 30 日之後 --&gt; 呢D leases 全部不受成文法續租影響<br />\n<br />\nbetween 1997年6月28日到期既 NK 同埋其他 NT Lots 一般都會按 Cap 150 自動續租<br />\n<br />\n除非係特殊用途契約<br />\n<br />\n你上面 cite 既 lot number 都唔係 Cap 150 附表1入面 --&gt; 咁就按第3條，視乎是否不容轉讓，判斷是否特殊用途契約<br />\n<br />\n言歸正傳，講到尾都係要成抽 title documents 拎黎研究"},{"pid":"db55df642c6b443181a7436a593a7d5dc05d0907","tid":650244,"uid":36324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ba8fd94ef063fc99051d8e058790e81bc57c106","tid":650244,"uid":72280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2874455a0cea0017f5a756c124f2e8cf7670b57c","tid":650244,"uid":72280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T08:35:13.000Z","msg":"頭先東方日報偷偷地更新左<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180502/mobile/bkn-20180502195628568-0502_00822_001.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180502%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180502195628568-0502_00822_001.htm&d=FtnGZSQXw2cpUIpZEyFXyp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=9b75b235\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180502/mobile/bkn-20180502195628568-0502_00822_001.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n運輸署發言人回覆指，已根據香港法例第230章《公共巴士服務條例》第20條，在2018年2月批准九巴使用其位於沙田及屯門指定兩所車廠為非專營巴士提供維修檢查服務<br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來運輸署又官商勾結發批文<br />\n但點解佢地無入紙去改個分地契呢🤣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T08:36:22.000Z","msg":"咁我係味可以拎住分地契去地政總署開 file?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T08:48:25.000Z","msg":"唔係想潑你冷水<br />\n<br />\n但你想開咩 file <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n運輸署署長有法定權力書面許可其他用途<br />\n<br />\n狗巴按照法定書面許可做個D用途就唔會違反地契<br />\n<br />\n香港既土地登記制度主要用途係判定優先權<br />\n<br />\n唔登記個書面許可，基本上唔會影響到個許可既合法性 (even if null and void, it's